text: Still looking into this. As far as I can tell, none else in my group has updated any programs or initiated any type of task such as disk cleanup that would have caused this to happen. I'm still reluctant about rebooting the server to apply the updates as there are about ten of them. If it was just one update from the previous month then I would go for it. But I want to know a little more before I do that. %40googlegroups.com
